13.1.22 'State'
---------------

     ATTRIBUTE State 24 string
        Users:                    'LR'
        Hints:                    'LR'
        Huntgroups:               'LR'
        Additivity:               Append
        Proxy propagated:         No

   This attribute is available to be sent by the server to the client in
an Access-Challenge and *must* be sent unmodified from the client to the
server in the new Access-Request reply to that challenge, if any.

   This attribute is available to be sent by the server to the client in
an Access-Accept that also includes a 'Termination-Action' attribute
with the value 'RADIUS-Request'.  If the NAS performs the termination
action by sending a new Access-Request upon termination of the current
